sw_test_results <- df %>% 
     group_by(item, site)  %>% 
    do(tidy(shapiro.test(.$similarity))) %>% 
    ungroup() %>% 
    select(-method)

res1 <- cor.mtest(df.short %>% filter(site=="fadn.gov.ru") %>% select(:), conf.level = .95, method = "spearman")
